com.github.upthewaterspout.fates.core.threading.instrument

Interface ExecutionEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExecutionEventListenerWithAtomicControl, NonReentrantExecutionEventListener, NoopExecutionEventListener, ThreadLocalEventListener, ThreadSchedulingListener

    public interface ExecutionEventListener
    Listener for receiving events from users instrumented bytecode. This listener is invoked from ExecutionEventSingleton, which itself is invoked by directly from new bytecode that is added to users classes. In practice, the Fates uses a chain of ExecutionEventListeners that start from the ExecutionEventSingleton and end with a ThreadSchedulingListener
